  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To investigate the association between metabolic syndrome (MS) and thyroid nodule(s).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      To investigate the association between metabolic syndrome (MS), body mass index (BMI),
      hyperglycemia, dyslipidemia, hypertension and thyroid nodule(s) or thyroid functions in
      euthyroid subjects. Screen for the risk factors that affect the incidence of thyroid
      nodule(s).
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
