  <eligibility>
    <study_pop>
      <textblock>
        People who received routain physical and laboratory examinations in the Health Management
        Cenre of QianFoShan Hospital from Jan. 2013 to Dec. 2015.
      </textblock>
    </study_pop>
    <sampling_method>Non-Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. People who received routain physical and laboratory examinations in the Health
             Management Cenre of QianFoShan Hospital from Jan. 2013 to Dec. 2015.

          2. signed the informed consent.

          3. Have complete clinical data.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. Patients with previous history of thyroid disease other than thyroid nodules.

          2. People with abnormal thyroid function.

          3. Thyroid ultrasound revealed patients with other lesions other than normal thyroid and
             thyroid nodules.

          4. Pregnant or lactating women.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
